    "English": "The fragile embryo of a <span class=\"name name-special\">Hungering Tendril</span>, still dripping with mucal butter. It wails and recoils when touched.<br><br>May be extracted from embryotic sacs with the aid of a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Visceral Synthesiser</span>.",
